data.description: Perfect horse Farm, 6 acres, close to downtown Madison, with fenced arena, pastures with four board black fencing, 2 stall barn with tac/feed room. Home sits off road with gate at entry and long driveway to rocking chair covered front porch with mature landscaping. Home opens to large Living & Dining area with great windows boasting natural light. Wood burning fireplace and built in bookcases. Kitchen includes long island and stainless appliances with tile backsplash. Back screened porch off kitchen with fireplace offers secondary entry from driveway. Guest 1/2 bath off kitchen area. Owner's suite is on the Main level with sitting area. Walk-in closets, double vanity, separate shower and soaking tub. Private covered porch off Master. 2 bedrooms with a bathroom and reading nook upstairs. Storage outbuilding with dog kennel. Creek in back. Foam insulation in the attic & fiberglass insulation in the walls. Crawl space incapsulated w/foam insulation. Windows & doors wired for alarm by EMC Security w controls in the laundry. 4 board treated wooden fence in front pasture. Combination of 4 board treated wooden fence, solar powered for wire electric fence. Laundry is plumbed for a utility sink. Solar powered remote control gate. Selling agent must be present at initial showing to receive full commission. If not present 1% will be given.
